Hillhouse Capital Management, Ltd.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 29, 2017 12:04 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Hillhouse Capital Management, Ltd.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Hillhouse Capital Management, Ltd is a privately owned investment manager. It provides its services to universities, foundations, and sovereign funds. The firm invests in the public equity markets and private markets across the globe with a focus on Asia.  It also makes private equity investments. It typically invests in the consumer, internet, media, retail, healthcare, energy and advanced manufacturing sectors. Hillhouse Capital Management, Ltd was founded in 2005 and is based in Beijing, China.


Floor 28, Building BPingAn International Financial CenterNo. 1-3 Xinyuan South RoadChaoyang DistrictBeijing,  100027ChinaFounded in 2005



www.hillhousecap.com







