Original Reference



Hillhouse’s Zhang Says Now One of Best Times to Invest in China
June 19, 2014 | Bei Hu | Bloomberg
        		Now is one of the best times to invest in China in 10 years as a slowing economy reduces overcapacity and forces companies to focus on generating free cash flow, said Zhang Lei, founder of Yale University-backed Hillhouse Capital Management Ltd.






